snippet.title: RPG Dragon Sinker - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Make a return to classic gaming in Dragon Sinker, a retro-style RPG!
RPG Dragon Sinker is now available for Android!

Google Play
[Premium]
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.dragonsinkerpremium&hl=en
[Freemium]
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.dragonsinker&hl=en
App Store
[Premium]
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1146377443?mt=8
[Freemium]
https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1146376710?mt=8

Join forces with humans, elves, and dwarves, and set off on a journey to slay the evil dragon, Wyrmvarg!
Employing 8-bit graphics and sound that hark back to the golden age of RPGs, Dragon Sinker brings a visual and audio feast to the table of hungry gamers starving for the nostalgia of the great classics of yesteryear!

©2015 KEMCO/EXE-CREATE
※All graphics terms, characters and elements are subject to change in the actual product.
